      • mazeSetup

        public Labirinto mazeSetup(Posicao heroPos,
                           Posicao swordPos,
                           Posicao dragonPos,
                           int dragonnum,
                           Posicao shieldPos,
                           Posicao javPos)
        Sets up a maze according to certain conditions in order to provide a proper testing environment.
        Parameters:
        heroPos - Position where the hero will be in the maze
        swordPos - Position where the sword will be in the maze
        dragonPos - Position where the first dragon will be in the maze
        dragonnum - Number of the dragons present in the maze (in most tests set to 1)
        shieldPos - Position where the shield will be in the maze
        javPos - Position where the javelin will be in the maze (only one is ever used in tests)
        Returns:
        An object of the class Labirinto according to the provided specifications
        See Also:
